featureType.title: NESP MaC Project 3.21 - spatial coverage of study areas from a publication inventory of ORE-relevant priority species: macroalgae species
featureType.abstract:
NESP Marine and Coastal Hub Project 3.21. This dataset shows the spatial coverage and associated metadata of a publication inventory of priority species of relevance to Offshore Renewable Energy (ORE) developments in Australia, especially in the Gippsland region.
This layer shows a subset of the publication inventory for macroalgae (seaweed) species. See layer 'NESP:NESP_MaC_3-3_ORE_publicationInventory_prioritySpp' for the complete publication inventory.
